Train/Test Split

set.seed(1)
split<-sample(1:nrow(SRBCT.data),  size=.75*nrow(SRBCT.data))
SRBCT.data.2<-SRBCT.data[c(top_10, "y")]
train<-SRBCT.data.2[split,]
test<-SRBCT.data.2[-split,]

# Tuning

                 ranges = list(cost = c(0.001, 0.01, 0.1, 1, 5, 10, 100)))
